The fact is that the tax inspectorate has quietly changed the procedure for notifying citizens.
Those who are registered in the "Personal Account of the Taxpayer" on the official website of the agency nalog.ru will receive notifications in electronic form.
The inspectorate automatically considered such Russians to be online users and deleted them from the standard, "paper" mailing list.
The innovation will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
Everyone else will continue to receive the usual letters.
